~~and moving between different topics mentioned in the aayaat and adhkaar.
~~this is what a person misses out on if he only memorizes a few soorahs
~~(especially the short ones) and adhkaar. varying what one recites is the
~~sunnah and is more conducive to khushoo’. if we study what the prophet
