~~wa mahyaaya wa mamaati lillaahi rabb il –‘aalameen, laa shareeka lahu wa
~~bidhaalika umirtu wa ana awwal al-muslimeen (i have set my face towards
~~the originator of the heavens and the earth sincerely and i am not among
