# keeping away from sin, because the prophet (peace and blessings of
~~allaah be upon him) said: “when any of you is fasting, let him not
~~commit sin…” (reported by al-bukhaari, al-fath, no. 1904). the prophet
~~(peace and blessings of allaah be upon him) said: “whoever does not stop
~~speaking falsehood and acting in accordance with it, allaah has no need
~~of him giving up his food and drink.” (al-bukhaari, al-fath, no. 1903).
