~~secret, so as not to attract accusations and the like. niyyah
~~(intention) in fasting (33) niyyah (intention) is a required condition
~~in fard (obligatory) fasts, and in other obligatory fasts such as making
~~up missed fasts or fasts done as an act of expiation (kafaarah), because
~~the prophet (peace and blessings of allaah be upon him) said: “there is
