~~intercourse with his wife but he breaks his fast by eating first, his
~~sin is more serious, because he has violated the sanctity of the month
~~on two counts, by eating and by having intercourse. it is even more
~~certain in this case that expiation is obligatory, and if he tries to
~~get out of it, that only makes matters worse. he must repent sincerely.
