# abu tha’labah al-khashani said: “whenever the messenger of allaah
~~(peace and blessings of allaah be upon him) broke his journey in a
~~place, the people would disperse in the valleys and mountains. the
~~messenger of allaah (peace and blessings of allaah be upon him) said,
~~‘your dispersing in these valleys and mountains is from shaytaan.’ after
~~that he never stopped anywhere but they all stayed close together, so
~~much so that if a cloak was spread over them, it would cover them all.”
