~~there are a number of important educational points we learn from this
~~story: 1 – the prophet (peace and blessings of allaah be upon him)
~~rebuked the sahaabi who had make a serious mistake by asking him, “what
~~made you do that?” 2 – enquiring as to the reason that motivated him to
