~~resurrection. having a dog at home has become a status symbol among many
~~rich people and high-level employees. the dog’s saliva is naajis
~~(unclean, impure), and the dog licks the members of the household and
~~their vessels. if a dog licks a vessel it must be washed seven times,
~~one of which must be with earth. how about if you realize how much
~~reward is lost by those who keep dogs? the prophet (peace and blessings
