~~your people have said to you, and their response to you. he has sent to
~~you the angel of the mountains, to do whatever you tell him to do to
~~them.’ then the angel of the mountains called to me, greeted me, and
~~said, ‘o muhammad, if you wish, i will crush them between two
~~mountains.’” the prophet (peace and blessings of allaah be upon him)
~~PageV15P0005
