# preoccupation with this world, so that the heart is enslaved by it.
~~the messenger of allaah (peace and blessings of allaah be upon him)
~~said: “he is doomed, the slave of the dinar and the slave of the dirham”
~~(reported by al-bukhaari, no. 2730), and, “all that is sufficient for
~~any one of you in this world is the supply of the traveller” (reported
~~by al-tabaraani in al-kabeer, 4/78; saheeh al-jaami’, 2384) – meaning a
~~little of something that will help him to reach his destination. this
