~~after a little while they go away, and the light of the moon comes back
~~to light up the sky. in the same way, the heart of the believer is
~~sometimes covered with dark clouds of sin, so its light is veiled, and
~~the person finds himself lost in darkness, but when he strives to
~~increase his eemaan and seeks the help of allaah, that cloud goes away,
