~~down.’” (saheeh al-bukhaari, 1099). when the prophet (peace and
~~blessings of allaah be upon him) learnt that ‘abd-allaah ibn ‘amr ibn
~~al-‘aas was staying up to pray (qiyaam al-layl) the whole PageV17P0061
# night, and fasting for days on end, he told him not to do that, and
