~~backbiting slander looking into people’s houses without their permission
~~two people conversing privately to the exclusion of a third isbaal -
~~wearing clothes that come down below the ankles men wearing gold in any
~~shape or form women wearing short, tight or see-through clothes wearing
~~wigs and hairpieces, whether made from natural or artificial hair, for
