# ‘abd al-rahmaan ibn abi bakrah (may allaah be pleased with him and his
~~father) reported that his father said: “we were with the messenger of
~~allaah (peace and blessings of allaah be upon him) when he said: ‘i fear
~~for you three major sins’ - three times: ‘associating partners with
