~~make a person sleep late, and whoever sleeps late will find it difficult
~~to wake up. finally, sincere devotion to allaah is the best thing to
~~motivate a person to get up for prayer, because allaah is the one who is
~~controlling all means of help. if a person has that true sincerity and
