~~cassette player in every home may be used for good or for evil. how can
~~we use it in a manner that is pleasing to allaah? one of the ways in
~~which we can achieve this is to have a home audio library containing
~~good islamic tapes by scholars, fuqaha’, lecturers, khateebs and
~~preachers. listening to tapes of qur’aan recitation by some imaams, for
