# tapes of fatwas may have a great effect on family members and help
~~them to understand various rulings, which will have an impact on their
~~daily lives. we suggest listening to tapes of fatwas given by scholars
~~such as shaykh ‘abd al-‘azeez ibn baaz, shaykh muhammad naasir al-deen
