# the lecturer should be a believer in the ‘aqeedah of the saved group,
~~ahl al-sunnah wa’l-jamaa’ah, adhering to the sunnah and firmly rejecting
~~bid’ah. the speaker should be moderate, neither extremist nor lenient.
