~~place of authority, and no one should sit in his place in his house,
~~except with his permission.” (reported by al-tirmidhi, no. 2772). i.e.,
~~no one should go forward to lead him in prayer, even if they recite
~~qur’aan better than he does, in a place that he owns or where he has
