~~24:27-28 – interpretation of the meaning]. PageV27P0027
# “… so enter houses through their proper doors…” [al-baqarah 2:189 –
~~interpretation of the meaning]. it is permissible to enter houses that
~~are empty if one has some legitimate business there, such as a house
~~prepared for guests. “there is no sin on you that you enter (without
~~taking permission) houses uninhabited (i.e., not possessed by anybody),
~~(when) you have any interest in them. and allaah has knowledge of what
