# the soul that is not active will stagnate. one of the most important
~~fields in which one can be active is the field of da’wah, calling others
~~to allaah. this is the work of the prophets, work which will save you
~~from punishment, realize your potential and enable you to achieve great
~~things. “now then, for that (reason), call (them to the faith), and
