# if a person is performing tawaaf (circumambulation around the ka‘bah)
~~or sa‘ee (between safa and marwah), and he finds himself in need (e.g.,
~~he is thirsty and needs to drink something, or loses one of his family
~~members and stops to look for him, or becomes tired and needs to take
